HEADWORD: Sea louse
<hw>Sea" louse`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Any one of
numerous species of isopod crustaceans of <gen>Cymothoa</gen>,
<gen>Livoneca</gen>, and allied genera, mostly parasites on
fishes.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sealskin</ent>⟦br⟧
